          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For obtaining the cross section of the 243Cm(n,f)",
                "the relation was used:",
                "Y=e*F*SUM(Gi*Ni*SIGi), where",
                "Y - count rate,",
                "e - detection efficiency,",
                "F - neutron flux,",
                "Gi - Westcott g-factor,",
                "Ni - number of atoms,",
                "SIGi - fission c-s at 25.3 eV",
                "   for i-th isotope considered, i from 1 to 7 for Cm.",
                "The fission count rate measured with the 235U sample",
                "can be expressed in similar way and the factor e*F can",
                "be determined.",
                "See ASSUMED data from REL-REF."
              ]
            }
          ],
